import { StyleSheet} from 'react-native';

const FirstStyle = StyleSheet.create({

    Titl:{
        marginTop:150,
        textAlign:'center',
        fontSize:45,
        fontWeight:'bold',
        paddingBottom:30,
        color:'crimson',
        shadowColor: "#000",
        shadowOffset: {	width: 0,	height: 12,},
        shadowOpacity: 0.48,
        shadowRadius: 10.00,
        elevation: 20,
    },
    text:{

        textAlign:'center',
        fontSize:25,
        fontWeight:'bold',
        paddingBottom:30,
        color:'gray',
        shadowColor: "#000",
        shadowOffset: {	width: 0,	height: 12,},
        shadowOpacity: 0.48,
        shadowRadius: 10.00,
        elevation: 20,
    },
    text1:{

        textAlign:'center',
        fontSize:25,
        fontWeight:'bold',
        paddingBottom:30,
        color:'crimson',
        shadowColor: "#000",
        shadowOffset: {	width: 0,	height: 12,},
        shadowOpacity: 0.48,
        shadowRadius: 10.00,
        elevation: 20,
    },
    Text:{
        marginTop:50,
        textAlign:'center',
        fontSize:30,
        fontWeight:'bold',
        paddingBottom:30,
        color:'gray',//crimson
        shadowColor: "#000",
        shadowOffset: {	width: 0,	height: 12,},
        shadowOpacity: 0.48,
        shadowRadius: 10.00,
        elevation: 20,
    },
    image: {
        width: null,
        height: null,
        resizeMode: 'cover',
      },
});
export default FirstStyle;
